      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels mostly like a burning sensation like food stuck in my throat, you know? and it started right after that pizza. i dont really want to go to the ER if i can avoid it, it's a huge hassle. do you think the arm thing is definitely serious or could it just be nerves from the discomfort? i'll just take the antacid for now and see if it goes down.",
